name: Modern Family Home
description: Contemporary 4-bedroom family home featuring open plan living, modern kitchen with scullery, and master bedroom with ensuite. Perfect for growing families with spacious living areas and practical design.

name: Compact Contemporary
description: Efficient 3-bedroom design maximizing space and natural light. Perfect for first-home buyers or downsizers. Features include open plan living, modern kitchen, and private outdoor living area.

name: Luxury Executive
description: Luxurious 5-bedroom executive home with multiple living areas, gourmet kitchen, and premium finishes throughout. Features home office, media room, and expansive outdoor entertaining area.

name: Coastal Retreat
description: Relaxed coastal-inspired design with emphasis on indoor-outdoor living. Features include covered outdoor dining, separate lounge, and bedrooms positioned for privacy and views.

name: Urban Townhouse
description: Modern townhouse design perfect for inner-city living. Two-story layout with living areas downstairs and bedrooms upstairs. Features include courtyard garden and integrated garage.

name: Starter Home Special
description: Affordable 2-bedroom starter home with smart layout and modern features. Perfect for young couples or investors. Includes open plan living, modern kitchen, and covered outdoor area.
